sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / ODH Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS (service-ca)
    participant API as KFP API Server<br/>8888/TCP REST<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP<br/>TLS (configurable)
    participant S3 as Object Storage (S3)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline Pod (executor)
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS/443
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    OAuth->>OAuth: Authenticate via<br/>OpenShift OAuth
    OAuth->>API: Forward to 8888/TCP<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)

    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS, Username/Password
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, Access Key/Secret Key
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>Argo: Watch Workflow CR

    Argo->>K8s: Create Pipeline Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    Pipeline->>API: Report status via gRPC<br/>8887/TCP, TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    Pipeline->>MLMD: Log artifacts/executions<br/>gRPC/8080, TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    Pipeline->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, Access Key/Secret Key

    PA->>API: Sync run status<br/>REST/8888, TLS (PodToPodTLS)

    API-->>OAuth: Response
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Operator Reconciliation

    participant DSPO as DSPO Controller

    DSPO->>K8s: Watch DSPA CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>DSPO: DSPA CR event
    DSPO->>DB: Health check<br/>MySQL/3306, Username/Password
    DSPO->>S3: Health check<br/>HTTPS/443, Access Key/Secret Key
    DSPO->>K8s: Deploy DSP components<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3: MLMD Metadata Access (External)

    participant Envoy as MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant OAuth2 as OAuth Proxy (MLMD)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    User->>Route: GET MLMD metadata<br/>HTTPS/443
    Route->>OAuth2: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    OAuth2->>Envoy: Forward to 9090/TCP<br/>plaintext (localhost)
    Envoy->>MLMD: Forward gRPC<br/>8080/TCP, TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>DB: Query metadata<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Results
    MLMD-->>Envoy: gRPC Response
    Envoy-->>OAuth2: Response
    OAuth2-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: Response
